TopicTitle: FSbattery Part missing after updating mods

Articles.Content:
I recently updated a few of my mods to 1.04 versions and after loading up my save file I get the message that certain spacecraft couldn't be loaded because the FSbattery part could not be found. This part is a fuel tank sized battery that wasd included in a mod but I have no idea which one. I used this battery in Power station ships and attached it to all my space stations so now all my space stations have been removed from the game . I can't seem to find which mod this part was from so I don't know how to get the part back in the game.

Any help is very much appreciated,

Shaun
It was included in Firespitter for your information.

It was included in Firespitter for your information.

You my friend are an absolute life saver. I've re-installed firespitter and all my spacecraft are back.

Thank you very much for your help.

Shaun
